style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%\">2900</span></strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">备注：</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">主推三盒，三盒以上可以送一桶蛋白粉或者奶瓶</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">六盒以上，可以送蛋白粉</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">+</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">奶瓶，可换成两桶蛋白粉或两个奶瓶</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">初步改善：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">盒</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; 1500</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">元</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">适用于产后</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月以上，乳汁不足以实现纯母乳喂养的女性，补充气血，增加乳汁供应。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">深度调理：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">盒</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; 2400</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">元</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">适用于产后</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月以上，乳汁供应逐渐减少甚至无乳的女性，补充气血，调理泌乳机制，追奶增奶。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">呵护巩固：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">9</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">盒</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; 3100</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">元</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">适用于产后</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月以上，乳汁减少或者回奶的女性，补充营养，持续母乳供应。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:3px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:3px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">十、催乳知识：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:28px;margin-left: 25px;line-height:28px\"><strong>1、</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">怎么知道宝宝有没有吃饱？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">妈妈感觉到乳房空空，没有胀奶感</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">宝宝小便次数少</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，颜色发黄</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">体重不增或者增长缓慢</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">宝宝刚吃完奶不久就哭闹找奶头</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">宝宝吃奶时间长</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用力吸允却听不到连续吞咽声</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">突然放开奶头啼哭不止</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:28px;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">孩子睡觉不踏实</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 25px;line-height:28px\"><strong>2、</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">母乳喂养对宝宝有哪些好处？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳是宝宝生长发育的首要营养品，母乳中含有免疫蛋白，可以增强宝宝抵抗力，母乳方便卫生，而且温度适宜，适合宝宝发育生长。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">①<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">增进母子感情</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳喂养是增进母子感情的枢纽，吃母乳的宝宝与妈妈的感情更为亲密，而且母乳过程能够增强宝宝的自信心，宝宝能够明显感觉到母亲对他的爱。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">②<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">促进孩子大脑发育</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">研究证实，母乳中的一种氨基酸牛磺酸与人类的大脑发育密切相关。这种氨基酸能使人脑神经细胞总数增加，加速神经细胞间网络的形成及延长神经细胞存活的时间。对于婴儿来说，母乳是其所需牛磺酸的唯一来源。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">③<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">预防儿童肝炎</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">研究人员发现，人工喂养的婴儿往往容易得一种虽不多见但能严重威胁宝宝生命的“婴儿代谢性肝病”。究其原因，是由于这些婴儿体内缺乏一种叫甲种抗胰蛋白酶的蛋白质。这种蛋白酶只存在于母乳内，牛奶及代乳粉中都不含这种酶类蛋白质。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">④<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">预防儿童肥胖</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　德国学者的一项研究结果表明，用母乳喂养大的儿童长大后肥胖的可能性相对较小。孩子接受母乳喂养的时间越长，到学龄阶段后肥胖的可能性越小。人工喂养的孩子，肥胖可能性比母乳喂养孩子高</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">倍。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">⑤<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">减少儿童变态反应源的发生</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">专家们研究后认为，这是由于母乳中含有大量婴儿必需的营养成分，可使婴儿消化系统和免疫系统健康发育，有利于抵御变态反应源的干扰，所以不易出现变态反应性问题。为此，专家指出：婴儿尤其是有变态反应家族史的婴儿，最好进行母乳喂养。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:25px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3、</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳喂养对麻麻有哪些好处？母乳妈妈产后恢复更快</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳妈妈容易加强与宝宝的亲情联系。在哺喂母乳的同时，母亲会分泌内啡肽，即著名的“快乐元素”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 52px\"><strong>①<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">利于子宫恢复</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0\">&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分娩后，当哺喂母乳时，妈妈会分泌一种叫做催产素的特殊激素，导致子宫收缩，使其更快地恢复到原来的大小。而这些宫缩并不感到十分疼痛，通常持续三到四天。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 52px\"><strong>②<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">减掉在怀孕期间增加的体重。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0\">&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这一切都会在母乳喂养的几个月里自然而然地发生。当您的身体为宝宝分泌乳汁时，会需要额外的卡路里，从而有利于减掉孕期中增加的体重。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 52px\"><strong>③<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有助于增进母亲健康</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0\">&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研究表明，坚持长期母乳喂养（</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月－</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月）会对母亲的健康产生积极影响。能够减少出现妇科问题的风险。催产素还有利于产后钙质的补充。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 25px\"><strong>4、</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产后少奶的原因是什么？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">专家指出，女性产后气血虚亏容易导致经络瘀滞，引起气机运行不畅、乳腺不通，妨碍乳汁的生成和排出</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">。女性怀孕时，气血一般自动调配到子宫用以养胎，生完宝宝后胎盘脱落，气血上行用于生产乳汁。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">气血充盈的产妇，乳汁充足。而气血虚弱，乳腺不通，一般都容易导致产妇奶少奶稀。专家指出，目前少乳产妇过多，主要与女性平时减肥、穿衣少、运动少、久坐等有很大的关系。加上生产过程中耗损大量的体力，失血过多，气血一时补充不足，就会导致奶少奶稀甚至不下奶。专家认为气血亏虚是奶少奶稀的根本，只有补足气血，疏通阻滞的乳腺才能开奶增奶。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 25px;line-height:28px\"><strong>5、</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">母乳分为几个阶段？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳是婴儿尤其是</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">个月以下小婴儿最理想的食品，母乳里含有婴儿需要的蛋白质、脂肪、碳水化合物、矿物质、钙、磷。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳根据产后泌乳时间的不同分为四个阶段</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">初乳（产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">天的乳汁，最为营养）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">过渡乳（产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5-10</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">天的乳汁）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">成熟乳（产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">天至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">个月）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">晚乳（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">个月以后的乳汁）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">产科专家指出，产后增奶要趁早，越早一天增奶，宝宝吃到的奶营养成分越高！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:3px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">十一、坐月子注意事项</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子不能洗头洗澡？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">只要洗头、洗澡后马上吹干或注意保暖，适度的清洁反而对亲子双方都有好处。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子不能外出、吹风？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">老一辈的观念认为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">坐月子期间最好不要外出</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">当然也要尽量避免看医生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子不能哭？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">这个说法是有道理的。产妇产后荷尔蒙急剧下降，伤口还未复原，又可能有哺喂母乳遭遇挫折、不知如何照顾新生儿等问题，容易感到忧郁。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子可以减肥吗？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">女性在生产后，身体正处于最虚弱的状态，需要充分恢复，同时在月子期间还要频繁母乳喂养和辛苦育儿，需要消耗很大能量，因此无论如何在坐月子期间都不要以任何形式试图减肥恢复体型，那样会严重地伤害到身体。不过也要注意，在月子期间亦不能享用太多高油脂和高糖分的高热量滋补品，那也会给日后的减肥加重负担。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子不能吃盐？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">摄取适量的盐是没有关系的，而且还可以提高妈咪的食欲，但若摄取过量，容易造成肾脏的负担、体内电解质不平衡。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子不能看电视？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">月子里可以看书、看电视，但时间不要太长。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子不能上网？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">对于年轻的产妇朋友们来说，年轻的产妇朋友应该尽量减少坐月子期间上网的时间以及次数，如果没有要紧的事情需要通过网络来处理，要尽量远离电脑，要远离电磁辐射。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、坐月子不能清洗外阴？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">为了预防产后感染，你在坐月子期间，应该经常清洗私处。保持外阴清洁，及时更换干净的会阴垫或卫生巾和内衣，以预防感染。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">9</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">、月子里出汗多正常吗</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">你</span><a href=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/11731.html\" target=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">产后出汗</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">的程度与你自身的体质、产程是否顺利等因素有关。你出汗的程度其实提示了你元气亏损的轻重。在产褥期，也就是我们通常所说的坐月子期间，如果你能及时调整身体，出汗多的状况多半可以自愈，恢复的快慢会因为你元气亏损的程度而有所不同。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">10</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">、剖腹产如何坐月子?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与顺产的产妇不同，剖腹产产妇</span><a href=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/1136412.html\" target=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">产后恢复</span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的时间更长，坐月子时也需要更加精心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">①请人帮忙：从医院回到家后，没有了医生和护士的帮助，你需要请你的父母、公婆、其他亲戚来帮助你坐月子。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">②坚持服药：如果你出院的时候，医生给你开了在家吃的药物，你要坚持吃，不要一回家就停止服药。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">③大量喝水：坐月子期间，你要大量喝水，以免发生便秘，同时，这也有利于你哺乳。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">④穿大号内裤：选择大一号的系带子的内裤或平脚内裤，可能会让你的伤口感觉更舒服。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑤注意卫生：你要特别注意产后的清洁卫生，特别是如果你是在</span><a href=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/1112327.html\" target=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">夏天坐月子</span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的话，这一点就更加重要。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑥保护伤口：伤口要勤换药，保持伤口和周围清洁干爽。休息时最好采取侧卧微屈体位，以减少腹壁张力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑦观察恶露：你的</span><a href=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/1110131.html\" target=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">阴道出血</span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和分泌物应该会逐渐减少，尽管恶露可能会持续近</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周的时间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑧注意饮食：做剖腹产的产妇，因为失血多，在饮食上要多吃一些补气血的食物，尽早恢复健康。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">11</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">、剖腹产多久后能过性生活?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">如果你在产后感觉很好，经过医生的同意，你可以在产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">周恢复性生活。但由于中国的许多医生都建议剖腹产后至少</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">年以上再次怀孕比较安全，所以</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">，你要严格注意产后避孕。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left: 0;line-height:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">12</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">、阴道松弛与</span></strong><a href=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/940364.html\" target=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">分娩方式</span></a><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333\">有关吗</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">尽管从阴道分娩胎儿的妈妈阴道发生了变化，会出现不同程度的阴道松弛现象。但并不代表自然分娩就是导致阴道松弛的罪魁祸首，因为妈妈在临产时盆腔的肌肉和韧带都会充分延伸，为宝宝的出生做好产道准备。</span><a href=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/long/15706.html\" target=\"http://baike.pcbaby.com.cn/qzbd/_blank\"></a></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:33px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">13、</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">月子里为什么爱出汗？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　产后出汗的症状与原因——</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　【产后正常生理性出汗】</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　产后初期，新妈妈出汗明显增多，往往刚睡醒或者稍许运动就会出汗，衣服也可能因此被浸湿，不过这类产后出汗不是病态，是正常的生理情况。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　【产后病理性出汗】</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　如果产后长时间出汗量大，那么就是病理性的产后出汗。一种是入睡后不自觉出汗，也就是产后盗汗。另一种就是出现白天的产后自汗，这种情况即使天气不热、衣服穿得不多，新妈妈也可能会满头大汗。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　产后常出汗原因</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　产后一至三天，新妈们出汗量确实很大，如果是夏天那么稍许运动衣服就可能湿透，这是因为生产后身体有不少生理变化，体内汗液旺盛所致。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">孕期皮肤血容量增加</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　妊娠期不少组织间的液体会渗透进血管，因此血容量会增加</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1-2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">成。而且妊娠期间雌激素变多、肾上腺功能旺盛，准妈妈基础代谢加快、血管扩张，这些都导致皮肤血容量提高。加之待宝宝出生之后，胎盘的血液循环会终止，子宫开始收缩，导致大量血液回到人体循环中。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">产后排出多余水分</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　而在生产之后，准妈妈的身体代谢、内分泌水平会逐渐降低到正常水准。为了降低轻心脏负担以及促进产后恢复，身体会排出体内潴留的水，主要方法就是排尿和出汗。在水分排出之后，体重也会急速下降，身材也在一定程度上恢复不少。所以说妈妈们不必过分烦恼，这是生产后的正常现象。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:19px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family: 宋体\">十二、产后知识</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">分娩后数小时不要吃整个的鸡蛋。但医学研究表明，分娩后数小时内产妇最好不要吃整个的鸡蛋。因为在分娩过程中产妇体力消耗较大，出汗多，体液不足，消化能力也会下降。若分娩后立即吃鸡蛋就很难消化，这会增加胃肠负担。因此在分娩后数小时内，应吃半流质或流质食物。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px;text-indent:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、产后应喝蔬菜汤。很多妈妈产后马上喝全汤催奶，导致乳腺导管堵塞，乳房胀痛加剧，不利于下奶。产后进补要根据身体状况，多数妈妈并不缺乏营养，最好先喝些清淡的蔬菜汤，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">天以后再喝全汤。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">推荐：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体\">原味蔬菜汤。将各类蔬菜主要是根茎花果不加任何调料煮汤，味道清香，可以当茶喝，在产后当天（剖腹产次日）即喝有极佳发奶作用。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">原料：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体\">黄豆芽、西兰花、菜椒（青椒、黄椒、红椒均可）、紫甘蓝、丝瓜、毛豆、西葫芦，每次选择</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">种以上即可。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">制作</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体\">：把各种蔬菜放入锅内，加入适量清水，煮烂后取汤水饮用。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">注意</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体\">！喝原味蔬菜汤的同时喝猪蹄汤、鲫鱼汤、鸡汤等会影响发奶效果。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">另外，产后最初几天，产妇几乎都有便秘的困扰。这是由于肠道和腹部肌肉松弛的缘故。所以，顺产的产妇从分娩当天就可多补充液体和吃些青菜水果来加以改善。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　</p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、<strong>误区：</strong>传统说产妇坐月不能吃青菜，否则</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">拉肚子</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">解释：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">老人们担心的拉肚子问题，很多时候指的是婴儿的大便呈绿色。婴儿偶尔会有墨绿色大便是因为食物残渣经胆汁消化，而胆汁是黄色并使大便成为酸性，排出后与空气接触，偶尔会变成绿色。一般喂母乳的大便容易偏向酸性，有可能成为绿便排出。另外，有些吃配方奶的孩子，排出的粪便呈暗绿色，其原因是一般配方奶中都加入了一定量的铁质，这些铁质经过消化道，并与空气接触之后，就呈现为暗绿色。还有：（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">）未吃饱的婴儿也可能拉绿色的稀大便，属于饥饿性腹泻。（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">）妈妈吃得太油腻，婴儿也会消化不良，拉绿色大便。因此妈妈的饮食要均衡。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳喂养婴儿，粪便一般呈黄色或金黄色，稠度均匀如药膏状，或有种样的颗粒，偶尔稀薄而微呈绿色，呈酸性反应，有酸味但不臭。只要</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">的粪便符合上面所说的，并且无其他异常状况，就不用过于担心。因此</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">某次绿色大便并不是妈妈吃了青菜，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">消化不良。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、产后三天内可以喝清淡鱼粥</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">产妇在生产完的三天内最好吃流质或半流质的食物。古代医家的建议是吃小鱼粥，为了通便可以另加一盘清爽可口的炒青菜；另外，小米粥、大米粥、鸡蛋汤、挂面也是好的选择。二三天后，胃口渐增，才开始进食其他滋补品。但胃口差时不要吃得太油腻，根据个人身体状况，早晚可喝热牛奶，每天吃</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">个蛋，然后慢慢再酌加鸡、鱼、虾、肉等，蔬菜与肉类要平均分配，均衡补充铁质、钙质、蛋白质等营养素和纤维，除了恢复体力外亦有助于乳汁的分泌。注意！产后的一周内忌食牛奶、豆浆、大量蔗糖等胀气食品</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　　　</p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、什么时候能活动：产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时可以在床上坐一会儿。如分娩顺利，产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时可以下床、上厕所。产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">24</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时可以随意活动，但要避免长时间站立、久蹲或做重活，以防子宫脱垂。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、记得及早给</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">吮吸乳头：分娩后半小时内让婴儿吸吮乳头，这样可尽早建立催乳和排乳反射，促进乳汁分泌。同时，还有利于子宫收缩。第一次哺乳时间以</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5-10</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">分钟为宜。产后第一天可以每</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时哺乳一次，哺乳的时间和频率自由掌握。产后第一天，产妇身体虚弱、伤口疼痛，可选用侧卧位学习喂奶。多数产妇分娩后头两天都还没下奶，此时不用担心自己是否有奶水，只要身体健康，每个妈妈都有足够的奶水。即使奶没下来，妈妈也要坚持让</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">多吮吸，因为吮吸有利于乳汁分泌。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时产妇要排尿：自然分娩的产妇，在分娩后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时即可排尿。少数产妇排尿困难，发生尿潴留，其原因可能与膀胱长期受压及会阴部疼痛反射有关，应鼓励产妇尽量起床解小便，实在有困难也可请医生想办法，如仍不能排尿，应进行导尿。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、随时留意自己的情况：产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">24</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时内若感到会阴部，或肛门有下坠不适感、疼痛感，应请医生诊治，以防感染和血肿发生。恶露会发出新鲜的血腥味，但如果发出恶臭，应立即告知医生，因为这表示可能感染了。另外，最好在恶露排出期间使用卫生棉或产妇卫生巾。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、、除了家人，亲戚朋友不要过早探望产妇和婴儿：由于刚分娩后的产妇需要静养以恢复体力，亲友最好不要在此时来探望。若来探望，时间也不宜超过半小时，要给产妇尽量多的时间休息。有慢性病或感冒的亲友更是最好不要来探视产妇及新生儿，以免引起交叉感染。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">10</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、产后妈咪特别注意不能混吃的食物</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">①海鲜与啤酒（有人喝啤酒能增加母乳分泌，有的不行）：海鲜是一种含有嘌呤和苷酸两种成分的食物，而啤酒中则富含分解这两种成分的重要催化剂——维生素</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">B1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">。如果吃海鲜时饮啤酒，会促使有害物质在体内的结合，增加人体血液中的尿酸含量，从而形成难排的尿路结石。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">②鸡蛋与豆浆降低蛋白质吸收：生豆浆中含有胰蛋白酶抑制物，它能抑制人体蛋白酶的活性，影响蛋白质在人体内的消化和吸收，鸡蛋的蛋清里含有黏性蛋白，可以同豆浆中的胰蛋白酶结合，使蛋白质的分解受到阻碍，从而降低人体对蛋白质的吸收率。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">③牛奶与巧克力易发生腹泻：牛奶含丰富的蛋白质和钙，巧克力则含草酸，若二者混在一起吃，牛奶中的钙会与巧克力中的草酸结合成一种不溶于水的草酸钙，食用后不但不吸收，还会发生腹泻、头发干枯等症状，影响生长发育。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">④土豆不宜烧牛肉：马铃薯烧牛肉，由于这两种食物消化时所需胃酸浓度不同，会延长食物在胃中的滞留时间，而拉长胃肠消化吸收的时间，造成胃肠的不适。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">⑤菠菜与豆腐易患结石症：豆腐里含有氯化镁、硫酸钙这两种物质，而菠菜中则含有草酸，两种食物遇到一起可生成草酸镁和草酸钙。这两种白色的沉淀物不能被人体吸收，不仅影响人体吸收钙质，而且还容易患结石症。医生建议，如果两者能分开吃，营养吸收会比较好。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">⑥萝卜与橘子（坐月最好不要吃橘子）易诱发甲状腺肿大：萝卜会产生一种抗甲状腺的物质硫氰酸，如果同时食用大量的橘子、苹果、葡萄等水果，水果中的类黄酮物质在肠道经细菌分解后就会转化为抑制甲状腺作用的硫氰酸，进而诱发甲状腺肿大。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">11</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、产后运动</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">分娩后的产妇内分泌发生了变化，全身肌肉、肌腱的弹性和力量下降，关节囊和关节附近的韧带张力减弱，使关节变得松弛，在此状态下，如果产妇过早过多地从事家务劳动或过多地抱小孩，会加重关节、肌腱和韧带的负担，容易使手腕、手指关节等部位发生劳损性疼痛。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">①产妇应避免劳动，但是可以适量进行少量运动。一般来说，产后</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">天就可以开始进行简单的腹肌收缩、仰卧起坐等运动，但要视情况，不能勉强，不能过于剧烈。喜欢有氧舞蹈的妈妈，则要等上</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">周才可以重新开始。总之，产后运动要持之以恒。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">②产后一段时间不能做较粗重的活儿</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">如：洗衣、提水、抬重物等，否则会患子宫脱垂。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">④如果在家中，恶露突然又转为鲜红色时，意味着胎盘原占据的部位未能妥善愈合，可能是因为您过度疲劳所致，应将此现象告知医师。医师可能会建议休息几天，以放松心情。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family: 宋体\">十三、下奶建议</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">①<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">自信是成功的基石：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">妈妈对自己能够胜任母乳喂养工作的自信心将是母乳喂养成功的基本保证。不论女性乳房的形状、大小如何，都能制造出足够的奶水，从而带给宝宝丰富的营养。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">②注意“食”效：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">新手妈咪应当保持每日喝牛奶的良好习惯（不要分娩后马上喝，否则容易胃涨，感觉肠胃好了才开始），多吃新鲜蔬菜水果。总之吃得“好”不是所谓的大补，太多的传统的猪蹄、鸡汤、鲫鱼汤中的高脂肪不仅会堵塞乳腺管，不利母乳分泌，还会让妈咪发胖，所以主要是吃得对，既能让自己奶量充足、又能修复元气且营养均衡不发胖，这才是新手妈咪希望达到的月子“食”效。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">③两边的乳房都要喂：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">如果一次只喂一边，乳房受的刺激减少，自然泌乳也少。每次喂奶两边的乳房都要让宝宝吮吸到。有些宝宝食量比较小，吃一只乳房的奶就够了，这时不妨先用吸奶器把前部分比较稀薄的奶水吸掉，让宝宝吃到比较浓稠、更富营养的奶水。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">④多多吮吸：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">妈妈的奶水越少，越要增加宝宝吮吸的次数；由于宝宝吮吸的力量较大，正好可借助宝宝的嘴巴来按摩乳晕。喂得越多，奶水分泌得就越多。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">⑤吸空乳房：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">妈妈要多与宝宝的肌肤接触，孩子对乳头的吸吮是母乳分泌的量佳刺激。每次哺乳后要让宝宝充分吸空乳房，这有利于乳汁的再产生。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">⑥<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">保持好心情：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">母乳是否充足与新妈妈的心理因素及情绪情感关系极为密切。所以，妈妈在任何情况下都要不急不躁，以平和、愉快的心态面对生活中的一切。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">⑦补充水分：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">哺乳妈妈常会在喂奶时感到口渴，这是正常的现象。妈妈在喂奶时要注意补充水分，或是多喝豆浆、杏仁粉茶（此方为国际母乳会推荐）、果汁、原味蔬菜汤等。水分补充适度即可，这样乳汁的供给才会既充足又富营养。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">⑧<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">充分休息，不能太累：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">夜里因为要起身喂奶好几次，晚上睡不好觉。睡眠不足会使奶水量减少。哺乳妈妈要注意抓紧时间休息，白天可以让丈夫或者家人帮忙照看一下宝宝，自己抓紧时间睡个午觉。还要学会如何在晚间喂奶的同时不影响自己的睡眠。每天争取能有</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时的睡眠，睡时要采取侧卧位，利于子宫复原。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">⑨按摩热敷刺激</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">按摩乳房能刺激乳房分泌乳汁，妈妈用干净的毛巾蘸些温开水，由乳头中心往乳晕方向成环形擦拭，两侧轮流热敷，每侧各</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">分钟，同时还可配合下列按摩方式：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">环形按摩双手置于乳房的上、下方，以环形方向按摩整个乳房</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">螺旋形按摩一手托住乳房，另一手食指和中指以螺旋形向乳头方向按摩</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">指压式按摩双手张开置于乳房两侧，由乳房向乳头挤压。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">⑩避免乳头受伤</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　如果妈妈的乳头受伤、破皮、皲裂或流血并导致发炎时，就会影响乳汁分泌。为避免乳头受伤，建议妈妈们采用正确的喂奶姿势，控制好单侧的吮吸时间，否则很容易反复受伤。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">饮食细节注意事项</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　<strong>　</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">少食多餐。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">不要吃盐，生冷的食物。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">半个月内避免吃青菜和水果。可吃点红萝卜。月子内要吃水</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">分少的水果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">半个月内禁吃鱼类和肉类，可以多吃肝脏等。因为疲劳的身体无法完全吸收鱼、肉的养分，结果过多的养分，只会加重身体的</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">负担，产生“虚不受补”的现象。应该到第三周开始吃。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">用麻油、姜和米酒料理食物。姜要爆透。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">生活细节注意事项</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">一定要休养一个月或一个半月。产后两周，除了吃饭和上洗手间以外，其他的时间一定要卧床。若常坐或起身走动，可能引起子宫下垂。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">准备两三条宽度约为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">30---40</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">厘米，长度可绕腹部</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">圈半的白纱布。产后要紧绑腹带，防止内脏下垂。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">前两周洗澡只能用温酒水擦澡。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　做法是烧开的水和米酒各一半，加一点点盐巴，用毛巾浸湿，拧干，在身上擦。第</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">三周起可以淋浴，满月后可泡澡。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">顺产者</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">)</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">洗脸刷牙须用烧开过的水放至温热再使用。可以使用保养品。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">严禁洗头。因为头皮不能着凉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">6.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">不能抱小孩。否则可能内脏下垂。喂奶时可侧躺着喂。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">7.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">不能为小孩洗澡，否则可导致腰酸</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">背痛及手脚酸麻。所以，给小孩洗澡的时要交给</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">LG</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">等人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">8.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">要有安静，舒适的环境。阳光太强时要拉上窗帘，保护眼睛。不能吹风，因为产后全身毛孔都张开了，吹风易引起头风及关节酸痛等，连扇子也不要摇。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">9.</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">月子期间不能爬楼梯，产后半年内不能提重物，避免内脏下垂。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">10. </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">不要流泪，否则眼睛将提早老化，可能演变为青光眼或白内障。少看书报和电视，一定要让眼睛充分休息</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">其他注意事项</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、<strong>喂奶感觉腹痛是正常的生理反应</strong></span><strong> </strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　母乳喂养可促进母亲的子宫恢复，喂奶时腹痛是子宫收缩的表现。每当子宫收缩时，子宫肌暂时缺血，小肚子一阵阵发紧，发硬，并伴随着恶露排出。因此，喂奶时腹痛是正常的。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、<strong>用正确的方法停止哺乳</strong></span><strong> </strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　一般情况下，应等到婴儿自己松开乳头后，方可拔出。如果妈妈因某种原因想中止哺乳，应先将手指放进婴儿口中，使其停止吸吮，然后拔出乳头。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、<strong>月子里易患腰痛、关节痛</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">　　产妇经过怀孕及分娩，内分泌发生变化，使骨关节，韧带松驰，钙质缺乏，容易引起腰疼，关节疼。因此，产后应加强适当的锻炼，注意补钙，不要过度劳累，腰腿痛经过一段时间可以自愈。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、月子里冷水确实不能碰</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left:25px;text-indent:0\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">新妈妈全身的骨骼松驰，如果冷风、冷水侵袭到骨头，就可能落下“月子病”。月子里冷水确实不能碰，即使在夏天，洗东西都仍然要打开热水器用温水。另外，开冰箱这样的事情，也请家人代劳。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　　　</p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、一定让宝宝多允吸</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">其实妈妈的奶水越少，越要增加宝宝吮吸的次数；由于宝宝吮吸的力量较大，正好可借助宝宝的嘴巴来按摩乳晕。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　 <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">妈妈应每</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">小时喂宝宝</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">次，但仍需配合宝宝的需求来喂。宝宝只要饿了就喂，喂得越多，奶水分泌得就越多；至于宝宝吃的奶是否足够的问题，可以检查孩子的尿片，只要一天至少换</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">片的话，就表示宝宝吸吮的奶水量足够了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\">　　<span style=\"font-size:16px\">TIPS</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">：每次让宝宝把双侧的乳汁都吸空，这样可以促使乳汁的分泌。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体\">按摩法</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><br/> 1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、乳房肿块按摩方法</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">用干净的毛巾蘸些温开水，由乳头中心往乳晕方向成环形擦拭，两侧轮流热敷，每侧各15分钟，同时配合下列按摩方式：<br/> 　　a、环形按摩：双手置于乳房的上、下方，以环形方向按摩整个乳房;<br/> 　　b、螺旋形按摩： 一手托住乳房，另一手食指和中指以螺旋形向乳头方向按摩; <br/> 　　c、指压式按摩： 双手张开置于乳房两侧，由乳房向乳头挤压。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:8px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">、乳头矫正法</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\"><br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: 宋体\">　　 有关妈妈乳汁不足的各类问题，其实都是可以改善的。可使用乳头矫正的方法：以左手或右手的食指及拇指放在乳晕两旁，先往下压，再向两旁推开；或是以乳头为中心点，采取左右、上下对称的方式按摩，这种方法会使乳头较易突出。也可在生产前注意乳房及乳头的保养。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><a></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;background: rgb(255, 237, 196)\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>',0,'2017-07-21 03:44:21'),(25,'红屁股相关资料','王者',2,11,'<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">红屁股相关资料</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">导致宝宝红屁股的原因</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　1、尿布更换不及时。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　婴儿吸收快，排泄快。小宝宝每天大约要尿10-14次，每次尿湿后，若没有及时更换尿片，就会导致宝宝臀部的皮肤长时间在潮湿、闷热的环境中不透气，从而形成了尿布疹。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　2、小屁屁清洁不当。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　现在一些新手妈妈由于经验不足，没有及时给宝宝的小屁屁做清洁，有些妈妈则是清洁过度，将宝宝小屁屁上的天然皮脂保护膜破坏了，导致一些细菌和污垢有机可趁。所以，爸妈帮宝宝清洁要适度，清洁太多或太少都会伤害到宝宝娇嫩的小屁屁哦。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　3、生理性腹泻或是母乳性腹泻。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　一些宝宝由于乳糖不耐受或是种种原因导致腹泻，这时候粪便及尿液中的刺激物质也会使小屁股发红。如果宝宝腹泻，爸妈一定要做好小屁屁的清洁工作。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　4、过敏。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　由于有些宝宝属于过敏性体质，而一些妈妈又给宝宝使用了含有较多化纤成分的尿布，或是经常使用一些含有刺激成分的清洁液、湿巾等物品，致使宝宝小屁屁的皮肤过敏，这也是造成红屁屁的原因之一。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">图片展示</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><img width=\"487\" height=\"274\" src=\"http://47.89.17.127:82/Public/ueditorpro/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170330/ffef51b5a2c64bd382d4158d01928577.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><img width=\"258\" height=\"344\" src=\"http://47.89.17.127:82/Public/ueditorpro/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"http://s03.lmbang.com/M00/4D/AF/eQ519FQZVByAC9E0AAJfO_hqML0742.jpg%21q.jpg\"/>&nbsp;<img width=\"204\" height=\"362\" src=\"http://47.89.17.127:82/Public/ueditorpro/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"http://img.pcbaby.com.cn/images/upload/upc/tx/kidsbbs6/1511/19/c5/15436292_1447905259067_400x.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">宝宝红屁股怎么办</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　宝宝红屁股主要是宝宝臀部被尿液浸泡，长期潮湿引起的，所以妈妈应<span style=\"color:red\">亲换尿布</span>，平时让宝宝臀部多暴露在空气或阳光下，而<span style=\"color:red\">不能用肥皂清洗臀部。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　1、保持皮肤干爽</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　在气温或室温条件允许的情况下，可以把尿布垫在臀部下面，让臀部充分暴露在空气中或阳光下，每日2-3次，每次10-20分钟，一般1-2天红臀就能有所恢复。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　2、及时更换尿布</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　对仅仅是局部皮肤潮红的轻度红臀，应保持臀部清洁、干燥，做到及时更换湿尿布，即使是一次性尿布也应定时更换，不能机械地规定8个小时换一次。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　3、涂抹禾护益加有机果油霜</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　如果局部皮肤潮红并伴有皮疹，皮疹如果有溃破，如果局部皮肤有糜烂或表皮剥脱，可以涂擦鱼肝油氧化锌糊剂。要是有继发细菌感染，可以使用禾护益加有机果油霜。 </span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　在涂抹油类应把棉签贴在皮肤上轻轻滚动，而不能上下涂刷，以免加重疼痛和导致脱皮。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　4、勤洗小屁屁</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　每次在孩子大便后或换尿布时，应用温开水洗净，吸干，再涂禾护益加。而不能用肥皂清洗臀部。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　必须注意的是，父母在为孩子清洗红屁股”时，应用手沾水轻柔地进行清洗，而不要用毛巾直接擦洗臀部，清洗完毕后要用毛巾轻轻吸干。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">禾护益加作用相关解释：　　</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">有机果油成分能在皮肤表面形成保护膜，阻断对皮肤的继续伤害，加速受损上皮细胞的再生，修复损伤的细胞间桥，加强皮肤的屏障作用。对尿布疹的早期皮损，作用快捷显著。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">产品有较强的抗氧化作用，效力强，明显缩短宝宝痛苦期</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">能够有效促进组织再生和疮面的恢复，同时具有抑制致病菌的作用。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">清利湿热积滞，红臀自退。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">改善局部的血液循环，促进局部皮肤的修复，又因直接作用于局部，效果更加迅捷可靠，且方便易行，若能早期应用，效果尤其明显。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">禾护益加不含羊毛脂成分的，不容易引起过敏</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">收到产品前，除相关护理知识外，可以让宝妈先这样做</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　发生宝宝出现红屁股时，可以用喝过的茶水清洗小屁股，茶叶中含的茶多酚是水溶性物质，用它清洗能祛除皮肤的油腻，收敛毛孔，具有消毒、灭菌的功效。用茶水洗完擦干后再涂一层油膏，能起到保护皮肤的作用。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　当宝宝屁股发生溃烂时用香油加热放点花椒粒，晾干后每次涂抹。还可以把鸡蛋煮熟后把蛋黄放到热锅里炒，注意要时时翻炒免得沾锅，炒成糊状出油后加放点香油，用纱布沾上蛋黄放在孩子的溃烂处，一天就见效。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">预防宝宝红屁股的方法</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　预防宝宝红屁股，应选用棉质的尿布，要舒适、吸汗、天然，尿布要勤换勤洗，彻底清洗后，要放在阳光下进行晾晒，便后要清洁臀部，要保证臀部干燥，给屁屁抹上禾护益加，最后再给他换上干净的尿布。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　1、尿布要棉制：对婴儿一定要用纯棉的白布做尿布，一是舒适、吸汗、天然，不象化纤可能对皮肤有一定伤害。二是可以更容易观察宝宝的大小便情况，因为大小便常常可以反映出宝宝的健康状况。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　2、尿布要勤换勤洗：家长一定要注意宝宝是否不自觉尿了拉了，以便及时换尿布。小儿尿后没有及时换尿布，特别是夜间不换尿布，或用一次性尿不湿一夜到天亮，这样长时间不换尿布，尿液对臀部娇嫩皮肤刺激会很大。尿布要勤洗，彻底清洗后，要放在阳光下进行晾晒，可以杀菌。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　3、便后要清洁臀部：新生儿的大便稀、量多，母乳喂养的新生儿大便尤其多。因兜着尿布，大便常沾满了整个臀部。有些父母或保姆在小儿大便后用尿布将臀部的大便擦去，而没有清洗臀部，使整个臀部仍粘附着大便，当再兜着尿布时，在潮湿有刺激物的环境下而发生红臀。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　4、要保证臀部干燥：清洗臀部后一定要把水擦干，然后包上尿布；注意不要认为给宝宝的臀部拍上粉，就使臀部皮肤干燥。如果臀部本来是潮湿的，拍上粉只是粉吸水变成块，不仅局部仍然潮湿，而且粉对皮肤也形成刺激。潮湿的环境使局部皮肤的抵抗力下降而发生红臀。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　<span style=\"color:red\">5</span><span style=\"color:red\">、给屁屁抹上护臀膏（最好选择不含羊毛脂成分的，否则容易引起过敏）</span>，最后再给他换上干净的尿布。 </span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">　　6、在换上新的尿布之前，先停几分钟，等小屁屁变得干爽。也可以用你的吹风机，调到常温那一挡，吹吹小屁股。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\">首页&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关于新生儿肌肤&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 天然呵护&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;成分介绍&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;案例反馈&nbsp; 在线订购<br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">天然果油防护 &nbsp;多效修护合一</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">守护新生宝宝的每一寸娇嫩肌肤</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">国际母婴护理协会推荐用品</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">美国原装进口 &nbsp;&nbsp;不含羊毛脂</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">有机植物萃取 &nbsp;&nbsp;食品级原料</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">绿色有机&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天然安全</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">执行GMP生产标准&nbsp; 美国原装进口&nbsp; 美国USDA有机产品认证</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\">抑菌止痒&nbsp; 滋润保湿&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 舒缓敏感 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;清热去湿&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 修护损肌</p><p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\">对抗⑥大肌肤问题</p><p style=\"text-align:center\">红屁股&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;乳头皲裂&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;湿疹&nbsp;&nbsp; 口水疹&nbsp;&nbsp; 淹脖子&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 肌肤干燥&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">新生肌肤娇嫩易损</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;多重问题不可小觑</strong></p><p><strong>宝宝红屁股</strong></p><p><strong>乳头皲裂</strong></p><p><strong>淹脖子</strong></p><p><strong>湿疹/口水疹</strong><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">来自美国的至纯果油精华&nbsp; 呵护每一寸新生肌肤</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加有机果油霜采用至臻果油精华，极致</span>舒缓<span style=\"font-size:13px\">修复新生娇嫩肌肤，让每一位宝宝都远离</span>红屁股、湿疹、口水疹 、 淹脖子、肌肤干燥<span style=\"font-size:13px\">带来的危害和痛苦，享受清爽的娇嫩肌肤；让每一位妈妈都能远离乳头皲裂带来的哺乳痛苦，实现与宝宝的美好亲喂时光。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加有机有机果油霜，是由美国农业部认证的植物精华成分，有机椰子油、有机乳木果油、有机葵花籽油，有机可可种子油，有机迷迭香种子油，及有机金盏花油等天然成分，采用了超微萃取技术，无任何油腻感，涂抹迅速吸收</span>，<span style=\"font-size:13px\">不仅能够迅速修复</span>抑菌止痒、修护损肌还能有效舒缓肌肤敏感、清热去湿，保持肌肤娇嫩。&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加&nbsp; 呵护每一寸娇嫩肌肤</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">抑菌止痒&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 滋润保湿&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;舒缓敏感&nbsp; 清热去湿 </span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">帮助受损皮肤再生</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">纯天然独特配方&nbsp; 有机安全见效快</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">有机牛油果果脂</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">纯天然牛油果果脂，极佳的人体皮肤亲和性，有良好的修复功效。牛油果含有丰富的甘油酸、蛋白质及维他命，润而不腻，不但能软化和滋润肌肤，还能抑菌止痒、清热去湿。果仁里提取的牛油果油营养丰富，含丰富的维生素E、镁、亚油酸和必需脂肪酸，有助于强韧细胞膜，修复受损的娇嫩肌肤。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">有机椰子油</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">天然椰子油85%以上的成分是大量饱和的脂肪酸酯，有利于皮肤吸收，能够减少经表皮的水分散失，起到保湿的作用。能防止皮肤老化，保持皮肤健康、柔软、平滑，配合牛油果脂等成分，可以有效修复受损的新生娇嫩肌肤。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">天然橄榄油</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">橄榄油富含不饱和脂肪酸以及各种维生素，极易被皮肤吸收，清爽自然，绝无油腻感，橄榄油中所含多酚类有抗氧化作用，可以快速抑菌止痒、舒缓敏感。配合牛油果等可以有效修复受损的新生娇嫩肌肤</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">有机金盏花油</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">金盏花油更适合新生娇嫩皮肤的护理，其可以做到温和补水，激活白血球促进血液循环，此外，金盏花油有超强的杀菌作用，能够促进受损肌肤伤口的愈合，改善敏感肌肤，促进肌肤的新陈代谢，搭配椰子油可以很好修复受损的新生娇嫩肌肤。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">有机可可脂</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">富含蛋白质活性成分，柔和皮肤，舒缓痛痒，滋润防止干燥。搭配金盏花、牛油果等成分对修复受损的新生娇嫩肌肤，保持肌肤干燥有很好的作用。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加6大优势 打造国际级专业有机果油霜</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，温和补水 舒缓破损肌肤</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">各种珍贵的有机植物果油精华黄金配比，能够有效做到温和补水，可以迅速舒缓受损的新生娇嫩肌肤，减轻因为肌肤问题带来的疼痛，实现健康成长。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">， 舒缓痛痒 柔和皮肤 防止真菌感染造成肌肤溃烂</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">以纯正有机认证的植物萃取调配而成，富含各种果油精华，可以做到舒缓痛痒，其蛋白质活性成分，柔和皮肤，滋润防止干燥，对修复受损的新生娇嫩肌肤，保持干爽有很好的作用。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，天然果油成分 安全配方&nbsp; 更适合宝宝娇嫩肌肤护理</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">全部成分采用天然有机植物，更适合新生娇嫩肌肤护理，可直接涂抹至宝宝肌肤，安全方便。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，同样滋润婴儿和成人的干燥肌肤</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">天然安全的果油成分无任何化学添加，任何肌肤适用&nbsp; 包括敏感肌肤及婴儿肌肤，当宝宝有湿疹等问题时同样适用。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，也可用于滋润嘴唇、手部等皮肤干燥部位</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">有机乳木果油，有机椰子油等成分都有卓越的滋润肌肤的效果，可以防止皮肤干燥，润泽肌肤，因不含香水、乳化剂及化学添加，同样可以适用于唇部、手部等皮肤干燥部位。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，可涂抹于整个乳房，保持乳房部位肌肤的湿润，减少乳房妊娠纹</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">配方具有至臻的果油成分，具有滋润肌肤，修复肌肤的作用，不仅可以用于宝宝红屁股、乳头皲裂，整个乳房部位，防止哺乳结束后的乳房紫纹。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">多重修护能力，还原新生娇嫩肌肤</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">口碑相传 好评如潮</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">专业研发15年 美国最受欢迎的有机果油霜</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><a></a><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; UPspring</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">是美国一家专业研发母婴护理产品的机构，该机构的宗旨就是给新生儿和产后妈妈提供贴心的专业支持，让新生儿不受痛苦和烦恼，成长更加健康。目前，UPspring已经研发出一种效果确切，有机安全的禾护益加有机果油霜，这款有机果油霜富含各种有机果油成分，可以快速有效舒缓止痒，修复受损肌肤，改善宝宝红屁股。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 13px\">经过十几年的市场验证，禾护益加已经成为美国新生儿必备的肌肤护理霜，不少妈妈在待产期就备好禾护益加有机果油霜，以备产后使用，改善新生儿及产后一系列肌肤问题。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">美国母乳协会推荐用品&nbsp; 不含羊毛脂&nbsp; 有效做到抗敏舒缓</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加所有成分均为有机果油精华，不含羊毛脂。目前市场上充斥着不少羊毛脂护臀产品，但是很多妈妈都不敢使用。因为，羊毛脂提取的是羊羔的羊毛，羊毛必须先浸泡在杀虫剂中来消灭羊毛中的寄生虫，经过这道必经程序提炼的羊毛脂，都会有一定的杀虫剂成分，这无论对于新手妈妈还是对于宝宝，都是不利的。而且很多女性对于羊毛过敏，在使用羊毛脂后会引起一些不必要的麻烦。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加与普通修护霜对比</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">纯植物</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">纯植物成分 更适合宝宝娇嫩肌肤</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">吸收快</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">黄金果油配方，更易于宝宝肌肤吸收</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">医生推荐</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">4000</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">平方米无菌净化生产，无添加</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">普通修护霜</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">抗生素残留</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">易有抗生素、激素残留，易引起蛋白质过敏</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">难吸收易反复</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">厚重，不易涂抹，不易吸收</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">有杂质</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">面临去除杂质的技术性难题</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加承诺&nbsp; 只提供安全 纯净 天然的产品</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加一直承诺专门为妈妈和宝宝提供安全、纯天然的修护产品，并向广大妈妈们承诺绝对不添加任何对身体有害的添加剂，让妈妈们放心使用。禾护益加是妈妈和宝宝都能放心使用的肌肤护理霜，可以有效修复和舒缓娇嫩肌肤，严格精选能够保护肌肤机能的成分，含有椰子油，牛油果油，葵花籽油等天然有机成分，而且通过了过敏试验，而且膏体清爽易推开，能够快速有效舒缓止痒，修复受损肌肤，改善宝宝肌肤问题。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">38</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">万肌肤修复案例&nbsp; 专注新生儿护理15年</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">新生儿屁股非常柔嫩，排便和尿不湿不透气造成肌肤破损，有的会造成真菌感染，宝宝整个皮肤都会溃烂，所以新妈妈应该给宝宝准备一只禾护益加护臀膏，帮助宝宝轻松健康成长。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Neonatal buttocks are very tender, defecation and diaper wet skin damage, and some can cause fungal infection, the baby will be the entire skin ulceration, so the new mother should give the baby to prepare a Wo Huyi plus diaper cream to help your baby easily grow healthy.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; From Idaho</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">我在待产的时候，就给宝宝备选了禾护益加，我一直想找一个抗敏性比较强的肌肤护理霜，很多宝妈给我推荐，决定试试这个，效果非常棒，我爱椰子油味道，后来我女儿出现了尿布疹，我找了很多产品，没有现成的。就试了试这个果油霜，结果女儿的尿布疹很快消失了。现在我和女儿都使用这款产品，对我们两个效果都很好。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:14px\">When I was in the process of giving birth, I gave my baby a choice of Wo Huyi Plus. I always wanted to find a strong anti-allergic hump nursing cream. Many Bao Ma gave me a recommendation and decided to give this a try. The effect is very good. I Love coconut oil taste, and later my daughter diaper rash appeared, I find a lot of products, there is no ready-made. Tried to try this cream, the results of her daughter&#39;s diaper rash soon disappeared. Now both my daughter and I use this product, for both of us.</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">From Idaho</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">中国区新生儿 &nbsp;效果也是棒棒的</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">舒缓红屁股效果棒棒的</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">对于宝宝的红屁股，刚开始我不是很重视，后来真的是真菌感染，蔓延了。看着孩子难受心疼死了，看到宝宝饿的哇哇哭也心疼，好难过。后来表姐给我寄来了一只禾护益加有机果油霜，看了看说明是非常安全，就尝试着用了，很快身体的事情出现了，宝宝的红屁股好了很多，也不抓挠了，而且还改善了我的乳头皲裂问题，强烈推荐给产后妈妈。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">李佳</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">不仅能修复宝宝红屁股&nbsp; 对宝宝湿疹也有效果哦</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">自从我买了禾护益加护理霜，感觉成了我们全家的公用品，我用来给宝宝修复红屁股的，孩子爸爸也经常用用（他的皮肤很干燥），我宝宝湿疹我也给孩子用，我感觉这款产品很棒，在国内很难找到一款有这么多用途的滋润霜，而且是纯果油精华，安全到食品级，我觉得这款产品值得推荐。多说一句，对宝宝湿疹效果确实不错。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">刘悦</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">调理好了宝宝红屁股 还能修复乳头皲裂</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">这是一款有众多用途的产品，我孩子红屁股比较严重，得到了很好的缓解，哺乳期乳头被孩子咬破了，疼的厉害，也是用了这款产品，使用后几天的时间，乳头皲裂就恢复的差不多了，当时是冬天，嘴唇干裂的厉害，我也拿来当唇膏，滋润效果不错。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong>婴儿皮肤的7大问题 家长一定要重视</strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span>新生儿皮肤娇嫩，妈妈在选择用品时就要注意选择无刺激的产品，注意涂抹宝宝的褶皱处，避免引起红肿；</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span>婴儿的皮肤容易受损，妈妈在选择宝宝的日用品和衣物时就需要注意选择纯棉柔软产品；</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span>婴儿的皮肤酸碱自控能力差，仅靠皮肤表面一层天然酸性保护膜来保护皮肤，防止细菌感染，出现问题及时修复。</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span>婴儿的皮肤发育不成熟，&nbsp; 真皮及纤维组织较薄，皮肤非常幼嫩、敏感，抵抗干燥环境的能力比较弱。</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp; </span></span>婴儿身体肌肤抵抗力差，婴儿较容易出现皮肤过敏，如：红斑、红疹、丘疹、水泡，甚至脱皮等。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加&nbsp; 让宝宝远离肌肤问题</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">拥有全球完善的母婴护理方案&nbsp; 专注新生儿护理&nbsp; 呵护宝宝娇嫩肌肤。</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">常见问题解答</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，这款有机果油霜多久可以见到效果？</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">如果处于红屁股初期，用禾护益加两三天就可以感觉到明显的变化，你会发现宝宝红屁股消失了，瘙痒没那么严重了。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，禾护益加吸收的好不好，这款产品对于我的宝宝安全吗？</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">这款产品每一个成分都是有机安全的，是植物性的，采用的是超微萃取技术，在涂抹本品后，大部分的植物油成分会被你的皮肤吸收。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，我是干性皮肤，手肘处非常干，可以用这款霜吗？</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">很多宝宝在使用后不久就调理好了。这时候你可以将有机果油霜用于干燥的部位。因为她卓越的滋润和修复效果适用于任何肌肤部位。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">禾护益加有机果油霜</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">产品参数</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">品牌：禾护益加</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">产地：美国</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">规格：60ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">适用人群：产后新生儿、孕期、哺乳期妈妈</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">储存方法：放阴凉干燥处</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">功效：有效修复新生儿</span>红屁股、湿疹、口水疹、乳头皲裂、淹脖子、肌肤干燥&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">成分：有机椰子油，有机牛油果，可可脂，金盏花提取物，有机橄榄油等</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">使用方法：长期涂抹可使肌肤滋润有弹性，减少红屁股带来的痛苦，每天使用两次，洗澡后涂在肌肤上，避免肌肤因过度刺激而干裂。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">海外直邮&nbsp; 购物须知</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">海外直邮 保证品质</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">中国海关的147号文22条明确规定：“个人物品进出境快件报关时需要提供进境快件收件人或出境快件发件人身份证件影印件和海关需要的其它单证。” 没有提供身份证的包裹海关不清关,清关必须要提供包裹收件人身份证才给予清关。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">海外直邮 注意事项</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">货品入境后要在中国海关进行正规的清关，正常时间为10-15天。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，客户下单付款并提交相关资料</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，海外发货国际物流发往国内</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，向海关提交报关资料，中国海关清关</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，转国内物流配送</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">，送达客户手上</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">直邮说明&nbsp; 购物须知</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">身份证信息是提供给海关的，用于包裹申报核对使用，身份证信息和产品都是保密的，绝对不会泄露，请放心购物</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">授权美国禾护益加中国区母婴顾问，为宝妈提供母婴问题在线咨询， 提供一对一的跟踪服务和母婴护理管理。针对母婴护理问题提供优质的咨询服务，全方位解决宝妈的母婴护理问题疑虑，让新生儿健康舒适成长。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">在线订购</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">滋润修复装</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">适用于新生儿</span>肌肤问题&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:13px\">，可快速滋润修复。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">盒&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 468元</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">肌肤滋养装</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">适用于新生儿以及肌肤修复的宝妈。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">盒&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 698元</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\">全家共享装</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">适用于家庭成员共享。因为也可以适用于肌肤干燥。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">盒&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1160元</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>',0,'2018-03-12 03:13:39'),(27,'迪斯唯尔产品知识','启航',2,14,'<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-align: center; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 32px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯维尔客服资料</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、妊娠纹部分</span></a></h1><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">妊娠纹生成的原因</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">人体在怀孕期间，肾上腺分泌了大量的糖皮质激素，皮肤弹性纤维与腹部肌肉开始伸长，增加了皮肤弹力纤维和胶原纤维的脆性，当皮肤弹力纤维和胶原纤维的伸缩度达到一定限度时，腹直肌腱也发生了不同程度的分离，就会引起弹力纤维和胶原纤维的断裂，于是，在腹部和其他撑大部位的皮肤上出现了粉红色或紫红色的不规则纵形裂纹。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">妊娠纹本质是皮肤变薄、真皮胶原纤维和弹性纤维断裂。不经治疗是不会消失的。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">容易出现妊娠纹的人群</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">没有好好控制体重</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不留心皮肤变化</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">觉得皮肤比孕期干燥</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">经常不自觉吃过量</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不喜欢运动</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">没有为皮肤做好产前预防护理</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">祛除妊娠纹的最佳时机</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产后三个月是消除妊娠纹的黄金时期，&nbsp;&nbsp; 产后1-2年是祛除妊娠纹的最佳时期</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">妊娠纹出现部位</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">妊娠纹大多出现在腹壁、大腿内侧、屁股和胸部，大致上是以肚脐为中心，形成多环形分布。有些准妈妈的臀部、后腰部、肩膀与手臂等处也会出现。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">纹路类型及其区别（生长纹、妊娠纹、肥胖纹）</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">妊娠纹&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 肥胖纹&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 生长纹</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">生长纹出现的原因</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">成因相同：都是由于结缔组织的撕裂而造成，这种纹路一旦形成就很难去除。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">生长纹成因：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">生长纹又称膨胀纹，是由于肾上腺分泌过盛导致皮肤弹性破裂，</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">形状颜色：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通常为多个平行的，首次出现呈现为红色，然后随着时间的推移逐渐消褪，生长纹表面细软，略有皱纹，比正常皮肤更光亮。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">生长纹出现部位：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">出现在臀部外侧、臀瓣、大腿上部、膝盖和腹部，也可能出现在胸部，手臂上部和腋窝。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">肥胖纹和妊娠纹的区别</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">肥胖纹和妊娠纹是不相同的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">肥胖纹成因：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">肥胖纹是由于骨骼和肌肉或脂肪的体积增加过快，超过皮肤的延长速度，真皮的弹力纤维被拉断，从而形成这种纹。体重增加过快的人就可以见到这种情况，许多在发育期的人即使长胖不是很明显也可以出现。即使减肥成功恢复了原有的体形。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">颜色：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">它开始是红色，随时间能够逐渐变暗，最后变成白色条纹。如果在发胖期间或怀孕的期间用一些增加皮肤弹性、促进胶原生长的药物可能会在一定程度上减轻或避免出现生长纹，但目前有很好的的方法。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">妊辰纹的预防方法有哪些呢?</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">均衡饮食:</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">怀孕期间应补充丰富的维生素及矿物质。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">由于胶原纤维本身是蛋白质所构成,所以可以多摄取含丰富蛋白质的食物。（肉类，蛋类，豆类）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">避免摄取太油、甜食(容易肥胖)、太咸(容易水肿)的食物。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体重增长</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在怀孕时体重增长的幅度上,每个月的体重增加不宜超过2公斤。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">整个怀孕过程中应控制在11至14公斤。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">使用托腹带</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">可以承担腹部的重力负担,减缓皮肤过度的延展拉扯。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">减少糖分的摄入,少吃含色素量高的食物也是很必要的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">多吃些胶原蛋白胶原纤维丰富的食品,以增强皮肤弹性,比如鳅鱼、鱼类。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">每天早晚喝两杯脱脂牛奶,吃纤维丰富的蔬菜、水果和富含维生素及矿物质的食物,以此增加细胞膜的通透性和皮肤的新陈代谢功能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、维生素E对于皮肤有抗衰老作用,富含维生素E的食物有卷心菜、葵花籽油、菜籽油等。维生素A、B2也是皮肤光滑细润不可缺少的物质。 当人体缺乏维生素A时,皮肤会变得干燥、粗糙有鳞屑,食物有动物肝脏、鱼肝油、牛奶、奶油、禽蛋及橙红色的蔬菜和水果。若缺乏维生素B2时,会出现口角乳白、口唇皮肤开裂、脱屑及色素沉着,食物有,肝、肾、心、蛋、奶。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">孕前注意皮肤护理</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">冷、热水交替沐浴：孕期沐浴时,坚持用冷、热水交替冲洗相应部位,促进局部血液循环。沐浴后,在可能会产生妊娠纹的部位涂上滋润霜。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">避免日光直射：日光的直射会加重妊娠纹,因此要预防妊娠纹出现或加重,日常生活中孕妇最好避免日光直射。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">祛除妊娠纹注意事项</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">建议在家做一些简单的运动(例如：抬腿运动)。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">勤于按摩容易产生妊娠纹地方(腹部、大腿内侧、臀部，以及胸部)，可以有效消除妊娠纹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">此时应多吃富含维生素C的食物，如柑橘、草莓、蔬菜等，还应多吃富含维生素B6的牛奶及其制品。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">保证充足的睡眠。让皮肤恢复弹性。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">祛除妊娠纹的运动方法</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">跑步去妊娠纹</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">跑步可以充分锻炼臀部及大腿，帮助将局部脂肪转化为肌肉，引淡化臀部及大腿的肥胖纹。你可以在健身房的加速跑步机上进行，将阻力从2挡调到3挡，并把车座适当调高。坐的时候，臀部稍微向车座的后面靠。当然也可以在户外慢跑或加速跑，有氧运动更能促进身体的代谢和废物的排除。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">臀部紧实收缩法</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">仰面平躺在地板上，腿部弯曲，双手平放在身体两侧，尽可能向上抬起你的臀部，收缩臀部肌肉。举起臀部并保持3秒钟，然后缓缓放下。此组动作重复15次，每周练习3次，4周以后你的臀部将明显紧致，肥胖纹亦会有所减轻。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">热敷涂抹法（产品使用方法）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">每天使用前用热毛巾热敷几分钟，然后在有纹的部位均匀涂上一些专用的去妊娠纹产品轻揉按摩，直至皮肤完全吸收。这种方法要坚持，如果什么时候想起来才涂，想不起来不涂，不坚持按正确的方法使用，任何有效果的东西都不会治好身上的妊娠纹。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">祛除妊娠纹食谱</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">西红柿</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　推荐菜谱：番茄汁</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　原料：番茄2个，水适量</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　做法：将番茄剥皮，加适量的水放入搅拌机中打碎即可。若想偷懒，买现成的保鲜装番茄汁也可以。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　营养小秘密：西红柿具有保养皮肤功效，可以有效预防妊娠纹。对抗妊娠纹火力最强的武器就是番茄。这是因为番茄中含有丰富的茄红素，而茄红素的抗氧化能力是维他命C的20倍，可以说是抗氧化、妨妊娠纹的超强战斗力，能够帮助准妈妈有效缓解妊娠纹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　爱心提示：西红柿性寒，如果空腹食用容易造成腹痛，所以准妈妈食用前应先吃点其它食物。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">三文鱼</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　推荐菜谱：烤三文鱼</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　原料：三文鱼肉150克、小番茄20克、香料少许。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　做法：先将小番茄洗净，待用；然后将三文鱼洗净，切块；然后用香料、料酒、精盐等腌制片刻；再取烤盘铺上铝箔，抹上黄油放入鱼块和准备好的小番茄，最后进烤箱烤熟即可。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　营养小秘密：经常吃三文鱼，可以起到减少皱纹的作用，从而有效缓解准妈妈妊娠纹。三纹鱼肉及其鱼皮中富含的胶原蛋白是皮肤最好的&quot;营养品&quot;。大量的胶原蛋白，能减慢机体细胞老化。经常食用，可使准妈妈皮肤丰润饱满，富有弹性，远离妊娠纹的困扰。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　爱心提示：在制作三文鱼时最好戒糖，控制精制淀粉，补充维生素和矿物质，以避免胶原蛋白被糖化而使准妈妈的皮肤产生皱纹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">西兰花</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　推荐菜谱：炒西兰花</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　原料：西兰花300克</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　做法：先将西兰花洗净分成小株，再将色拉油倒入锅中加热，加入西兰花、盐及胡椒粉，翻炒数下即可。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　营养小秘密：西兰花中含有丰富的维生素A、维生素C和胡萝卜素，能增强皮肤的抗损伤能力、这将有助于保持皮肤弹性，可以使准妈妈远离妊娠纹的困扰。很多准妈妈以为番茄是含维生素C最丰富的蔬菜，其实，西兰花的维生素C几乎是番茄的4倍。而丰富的维生素C不但能增强准妈妈免疫力，保证胎宝宝不受病菌感染，还能增强皮肤弹性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　爱心提示：准妈妈每周宜吃3次西兰花，但西兰花中含有丰富的叶酸，叶酸性质不稳定，为保证叶酸不被破坏，西兰花以少油快炒为佳。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">海带&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　推荐菜谱：松仁海带</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　原料：松子仁5克，水发海带1克，鸡汤、盐各少许</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　制作：松子仁用清水洗净；再将水发海带洗净，切成细丝；然后将锅置火上，放入鸡汤、松子仁、海带丝用文火煨熟，加盐调味即成。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　营养小秘密：海带中含有丰富的矿物质，常吃能够调节血液中的酸碱度，防止皮肤过多分泌油脂，而且海带富含碘、钙、磷、硒等多种人体必需的微量元素，其中钙含量是牛奶的10倍，含磷量比所有的蔬菜都高。海带还含有丰富的胡萝卜素、维生素B1等维生素，可以有效防止皮肤老化，有效缓解妊娠纹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　爱心提示：海带性寒，对于准妈妈来说，烹饪时宜加些性热的姜汁、蒜蓉等，而且不宜放太多油。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: Wingdings;\">n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">黄豆</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　推荐菜谱：黄豆排骨汤</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　原料：黄豆100克、猪排骨250克、精盐适量</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　做法：先把猪排骨洗净，切成小块，置于火上，加清水适量，旺火煮沸。再把黄豆、猪排骨放入锅内，加盖，转为温火煲3小时后，点入精盐调味即可。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　营养小秘密：黄豆中所富含的维生素E能够破坏自由基的化学活性，不仅能抑制皮肤衰老，更能增加皮肤弹性，防止色素沉着于皮肤。维生素与蛋白质是美化肌肤、润泽容颜的源泉，是人体健康和美丽必不可少的物质基础。黄豆中含有丰富的维生素A、B、D、E和多种人体不能合成但又必需的氨基酸。所以常食黄豆，可以使皮肤细敕、白皙、润泽，有效防止妊娠纹的出现。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">　　爱心提示：如若将生黄豆炒熟吃，不仅会妨碍准妈妈对蛋白质的吸收，还会对健康产生有害影响。正确的吃法是将黄豆浸泡后再炒食或做成汤食用。</span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、迪斯唯尔产品知识部分</span></a></h1><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产品名称：迪斯唯尔</span></strong></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产品信息</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">名 &nbsp;称：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯维尔-----Digeswell</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规 &nbsp;格：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;120ml/盒</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产 &nbsp;地：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">美国</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">使用方法：</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">每天使用前用热毛巾热敷几分钟，取足够用量在有纹的部位均匀涂抹轻揉按摩，直至皮肤完全吸收。每天至少2次涂抹基础上，涂抹次数越多越好。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">各部位按摩方法</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">腹部：以肚脐为中心双手重叠放在腹部，以顺时针方向轻柔按摩直至吸收（最少5分钟）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">胸部：左手按摩右乳房，右手按摩左乳房，由乳房下方锁骨方向按摩5分钟；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">臀部：双手分别放在臀部两侧，由下往上，由内往外提拉按摩5分钟；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">腿部：双手掌放在膝盖上，由膝盖缓慢推至大腿内侧，重复约5分钟。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平时多给含维生素多的水果，坚持运动出汗，多涂抹，最主要的是涂抹之前一定要热敷。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注意事项：</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本品不能服用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本品切勿将本品置于高温处</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对本品过敏者禁用，过敏体质者慎用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本品性状发生改变时禁止使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请将本品放在儿童不能接触的地方。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">针对人群：</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">适合肥胖纹、生长纹及产后有妊娠纹的年轻女性群体。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产品主要成分：</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">金盏花、芦荟汁、罗莎馏分油,乳木果、乳化蜡NF,洁食蔬菜甘油,金缕梅、天然可可脂、维生素E、苯氧乙醇、棕榈硬脂酸,芒果黄油、甜橙精油、多糖胶、薰衣草 精油、甘露聚糖、有机黑柳树皮提取物、迷迭香、印楝,四钠EDTA和柠檬酸。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">可以促进皮肤底层的血液循环和新陈答谢，通过3-5天妊娠纹部位的按摩吸收，可以达到击退沉淀色素和淡化纹路的效果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在不断淡化纹路的同时，活性成分也在不断在渗透，从表层肌肤渗入到皮肤底层，不断生成细胞再生所需要的胶原蛋白成分。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对抗肌肤失调成分不断作用，结缔组织的重建和纤维组织的修复也会在这个时期完成 。肌肤已经恢复到产前表层的80%。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过产品的滋润和紧致成分的作用，明显能感觉到肌肤变的不断润滑和紧致。这个时期继续按摩吸收，恢复少女肌肤魅力。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯维尔是什么？</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯维尔是美国顶尖的产后妊娠纹修复霜，经20科技研发，于 2006年研发成功并上市。迪斯维尔是一款专注于纤维再生的祛除妊娠纹霜体配方。采用美国CIP高活性静压技术将MHA 元素、金盏花、乳木果、芒果黄油、芦荟、维生素e、维生素A和精油等成分精华完美配比。具有深层纤维增长，表层滋润肌肤，全面作用于去除纹路、色素沉着与皮肤的全面修复改善作用。始终坚持天然农场养殖，甄选最优质原料，直接作用于妊娠纹机体。产品通过美国USDA体系和美国FDA双重认证，安全有效，作用直接有效的解决妊娠纹问题。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯维尔安全吗？</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">原料100%纯天然：始终坚持天然农场养殖，甄选最优质的可可脂、金盏花、乳木果、芦荟、维生素e、维生素A和精油成分精华，采取的是最科学的萃取技术。产品通过美国USDA体系和美国FDA双重认证，安全有效。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">Biotegrity</span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">公司是美国顶尖的FDA授权批准的的产后修护产品生产机构，从产品原料的甄选到密封生产，严格把控每一个环节，打造最专业的去除妊娠纹产品。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯维尔是哪个厂家生产的？</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 21px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">Biotegrity</span><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">公司是美国顶尖的FDA授权批准的的产后修护产品生产机构，从产品原料的甄选到密封生产，严格把控每一个环节，打造最专业的去除妊娠纹产品。</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">11.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯唯尔产品技术解读</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"></spa