; line-height: 19.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">还原肌肤新生能力</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-align: justify; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">激活作用于</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">结缔组织皮肤中细胞外间质的蛋白质复合物的生成和高活性元素吸收，促进纤维细胞快速生长，全面覆盖代谢老化纤维细胞肌肤 ，从而直接祛除妊娠纹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"></span><br/></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 56px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><a style=\"color: rgb(45, 114, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">12.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">迪斯唯尔作用机理</span></a></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 32px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">双向作用力&nbsp; 深层纤维增长&nbsp; 表层滋润肌肤</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; marg