</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">迪斯唯尔是美国原装进口的产品，研发和生产都是都是从美国完成，产品直接从美国厂家发出，成分和效果都相对有保障，而且相对于国内很多同类产品来说</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，迪斯唯尔是不算贵，因为其他宝妈的使用反馈不错，所以才推荐给你的</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：成分安全吗？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个宝妈啊可以放心孕期和哺乳期都可以使用，成分绝对安全。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：那怎么购买啊？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">迪斯唯尔是美国原装进口的，在美国发出后通过香港海关才能进入国内，我这边有相关的官方证书和认证证件，可以帮你申请登记，百分百保证正品（<span style=\"color: red;\">美国自由销售正品和各种认证</span>）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">使用一个周期后就可以看到明显的效果，妊娠纹不及时修复的话，发展到中后期修复周期更长，建议你及时进行调理，</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">客户：我先买一瓶看看有没有效果吧</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span>15-28<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天是人体一个代谢周期，通过已经修复的宝妈反馈，周期修复效果更好，所以按照周期修复，效果更好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：这个产品真的这么有效果啊</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">咱这个是通过美国</span>FDA<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span>USDA<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认证的，从</span>06<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年上市至今</span>10<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多年了，很多宝妈都用过，效果很安全稳定，朋友圈里都是真实修复案例，宝妈可以看下，而且修复期间我会一直跟踪指导的。<span style=\"color: red;\">（附带反馈图）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：不管用怎么办？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目前还没有收到无效的反馈，很多宝妈使用后，都反馈效果达到心理预期，所以才推荐给你，而且受到产品后我会跟踪指导你使用，效果会更好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：我在考虑考虑吧</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">好的，是考虑价格还是产品效果？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：都有</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：价格方面，咱这个产品是有绝对优势的，据我了解，现在修复妊娠纹的产品基本上都是国内的，而且产品价格绝对比咱们的高。而且成分效果没保障。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果方面的话，朋友圈的真实案例你也看到了，效果都非常棒，而且产品都是美国原装进口的，美国对成分和效果都要求比较高，宝妈可以放心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：太贵了，便宜些，我买一个周期的</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">价格都是美国厂家官方统一规定的，我没有调价的权限，这样吧，我申请多赠送你一盒多酚提苏活力片。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 32px; font-family: 宋体;\">范老师：你可以先拿一个周期两盒用着，等淡化了再来拿第二周期进行巩固，我只能说越早修复越好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：这个是干嘛的？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">这个是淡化色素纹路和修复底层腺细胞的，和修护霜搭配使用效果更好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：好吧，那我先购买一个周期吧，那怎么发货呢</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">微信或支付宝转款后，留下联系方式姓名地址，今天就可以申请登记、安排发货</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">客户：可以货到付款吗</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">不可以的，所有正规进口产品美国经香港海关检验都是需要全款支付的，海关官方不支持货到付款的发货形式，收到之后快递会有香港海关发货记录可以确保产品百分百正品的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">客户：我不太放心</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">现在微信都是实名认证，转账也是有记录存在的，这个放心就可以</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：好的，相信你一次，发货吧（转账）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宝妈，微信还是支付宝方便？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：微信吧，直接转账就可以吗？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（转账）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">跨境购物需要提供身份证号码，</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宝妈提供一下和姓名相对的身份证号。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">客户：怎么使用呢</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">范老师：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">收到产品后及时联系我，我指导使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; white-sp